{"tid":1507394,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[中學生注意] 當校長老師發表撐警言論，記得答佢：「切勿請政治帶入校園。」","createTime":"2019-08-26T06:35:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T05:22:02.000Z","uid":71237,"like":75,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"aae549b89fe40ffab141466889a137c901170f92","tid":1507394,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T06:35:55.000Z","msg":"政務司司長張建宗強調，<span style=\"color: red;\">學校絕不是表達政治主張或訴求的地方，不應把政治凌駕教育之上。學校不應成為政治角力的場地，任何成年人都不應向仍在求學的孩子，灌輸其政治看法，甚或威逼利誘學生參與政治化的活動。</span>不少家長擔心子女會因立場不同，或因家人的職業和背景等而在學校被仇視欺凌。他強調，政府和學校對於任何校園欺凌堅持「零容忍」，呼籲各界以保護兒童為大前提，<span style=\"color: red;\">拒絕把政治爭拗帶入校園。</span><br />\n<br />\n教育局局長楊潤雄又指，<span style=\"color: red;\">任何人都不應以學校作為表達政治訴求的場地，將年輕的學生捲入政治漩渦。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀：<br />\n[集思廣益] 9月2日中學生有咩應該做、有咩唔應該做？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1506013/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1506013/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"19eec2936c65aa29cf726cb56a8e6bf9e1084769","tid":1507394,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T06:36:17.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借個post宣傳一下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4GJMrJb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4GJMrJb.jpg&h=cb7c9807&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n901 和你塞  13:00 見   <a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY%2Fo5m3Xr9SEp5dZU2qkndIk%3D&h=d507cd5b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"},{"pid":"16c3af628e006c6fad38e295fd33413339668df5","tid":1507394,"uid":71237,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T06:39:28.000Z","msg":"老師最鍾意雙重標準。<br />\n你反對政府就唔得，佢發表撐警言論就得。"},{"pid":"7dd1ddf2a5624b0fd617c90040c8212787ea41bb","tid":1507394,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T06:39:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">【眾籌 Google 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告</span><br />\n<a href=\"https:/